{"type":"message","id":"2b7db6e6","parentId":"ff8ef2e1","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:18:43.281Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b536880d1fca0c4d7a6772149a69\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-27 08:18 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b536880d1fca0c4d7a6772149a69]\nou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e: 使用find-skill和全网搜索，帮我找到可以运营咸鱼的skill"}],"timestamp":1774570723247}}
{"type":"message","id":"5b134c09","parentId":"2b7db6e6","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:24:00.879Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在需要找可以运营闲鱼的skill，首先看已有的技能列表，有一个xianyu-auto-reply的技能对吧？不过用户说要用find-skill和全网搜索，首先我应该先调用find-skills工具，搜索关键词是闲鱼、xianyu、咸鱼这些对吧？然后可能还要web搜索确认有没有其他相关的skill？不对，先看find-skill的工具，哦对，有个find-skills的skill，首先我需要先调用find-skills工具，搜索query是咸鱼 闲鱼 xianyu 自动回复 运营。首先，第一步调用find-skills工具？不对，工具列表里有个叫find-skills的skill，它的SKILL.md在~/.openclaw/skills/find-skills/SKILL.md对吧？按照技能使用规则，当需要找技能的时候，应该先读取这个find-skills的SKILL.md对吧？哦对，首先，用户需要找闲鱼运营的skill，所以触发了find-skills这个技能，所以首先应该用read工具读取find-skills的SKILL.md文件，然后按照它的说明来搜索。\n\n等下，先看available_skills里的find-skills：\n<skill>\n    <name>find-skills</name>\n    <description>ClawHub技能搜索和发现工具，支持搜索、筛选、发现适合的技能。支持按功能、分类、评分、下载量筛选，提供技能详情、使用说明、安装指引。当用户需要找某个功能的技能、探索新技能时使用。</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw\\skills\\find-skills\\SKILL.md</location>\n</skill>\n对，所以首先要读取这个SKILL.md，了解怎么使用这个技能来搜索闲鱼相关的skill。所以第一步调用read工具，路径是~/.openclaw/skills/find-skills/SKILL.md对吧？不对，路径里的反斜杠要转成正斜杠？或者在Windows下也可以？不过直接用给出的location就行，把反斜杠换成正斜杠或者直接用？哦，read工具的path参数可以接受相对或者绝对路径，所以先读取这个SKILL.md。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_g12od5dnoo789e7n6f51hlqm","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/find-skills/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":24881,"output":990,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25871,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774570723282,"responseId":"021774571024392eff6165463a2ce5f140dae355499e179dbd3af"}}
{"type":"message","id":"55345958","parentId":"5b134c09","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:24:00.894Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_g12od5dnoo789e7n6f51hlqm","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: find-skills\ndescription: ClawHub技能搜索和发现工具，支持搜索、筛选、发现适合的技能。支持按功能、分类、评分、下载量筛选，提供技能详情、使用说明、安装指引。当用户需要找某个功能的技能、探索新技能时使用。\n---\n\n# Find Skills 技能搜索工具\n\n## 核心功能\n- 🔍 **技能搜索**：按关键词搜索ClawHub上的所有公开技能\n- 📊 **筛选功能**：按分类、评分、下载量、更新时间筛选技能\n- 📝 **技能详情**：查看技能的完整描述、功能说明、使用方法\n- ⭐ **评分系统**：查看其他用户对技能的评分和评价\n- 📈 **热门推荐**：推荐热门、高评分、新上线的技能\n- 📦 **一键安装**：直接安装选中的技能，自动解决依赖\n\n## 搜索语法\n- 普通关键词搜索：`find-skills \"web search\"`\n- 按分类搜索：`find-skills category:productivity`\n- 按评分筛选：`find-skills \"AI\" rating:>4.5`\n- 按下载量筛选：`find-skills \"git\" downloads:>1000`\n- 组合搜索：`find-skills \"frontend\" category:development rating:>4.0`\n\n## 使用示例\n```python\n# 搜索技能\nresults = search_skills(\"tavily search\", category=\"tools\", rating_min=4.0)\nfor skill in results:\n    print(f\"{skill['name']} - {skill['description']}\")\n    print(f\"评分: {skill['rating']} ⭐ 下载量: {skill['downloads']}\")\n\n# 安装技能\ninstall_skill(\"tavily-search\")\n```\n\n## 触发场景\n- 用户需要查找具有特定功能的技能\n- 想要探索新的技能，扩展功能\n- 寻找热门、高评分的优质技能\n- 需要了解某个技能的详细信息和使用方法\n- 比较多个同类技能的优缺点，选择最合适的\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774571040890}}
{"type":"message","id":"695cb938","parentId":"55345958","timestamp":"2026-03-27T00:24:07.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n好的，现在我已经知道了find-skills的使用方法，接下来我需要搜索闲鱼相关的技能。首先，用户需要的是可以运营咸鱼的skill，关键词应该是\"咸鱼\"、\"闲鱼\"、\"xianyu\"、\"自动回复\"、\"运营\"这些对吧？现在我需要调用find-skills的搜索功能？不对，哦，原来find-skills是通过clawhub CLI来搜索的对吧？对，之前的clawhub skill也提到过用ClawHub CLI来搜索、安装技能。哦对，我应该用exec工具运行clawhub search命令来搜索相关的技能。\n首先，运行clawhub search xianyu 闲鱼 咸鱼 运营 自动回复，这样就能找到相关的技能了。对吧？\n所以现在调用exec工具，command是clawhub search \"xianyu 闲鱼 咸鱼 运营 自动回复\"。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d5f39tkabhyqihpe87avopsq","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"xianyu 闲鱼 咸鱼 运营 自动回复\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":1506,"output":439,"cacheRead":24376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26321,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774571040894,"responseId":"021774571041325d619db30bd0c9858e230a26bb16935251e1d5a"}}
